creator: ArtStyle
descriptionHtml:
"Radio Latvia" it is a simple and easy to use application, but complete and very powerful, that you can install for free to enjoy a variety of Latvia radios, 24 hours, from anywhere in the world.
Enjoy the main AM radios and FM radios of Latvia with the best and most varied programming from your mobile or tablet: the most varied and wide range of music, sports, and the latest news from Latvia and the world.
The application is updated constantly and we are adding new stations.
No useless ornaments, no space consumption functionalities, just Online Radio!

Features:
- FM/AM & Online radio stations from Latvia
- Save your favorite radio stations
- Instant search
- Listen radios in the background
- Sleep timer
- Name of singers and songs
- Instant playback and premium quality
- Share with friends via Facebook, Twitter or Email
- Available horizontal and vertical orientation
